steps.name: a request is prepared to create an employee
a POST call is made to create an employee
the status code for the created employee is 201
the employee created contains key "Message" and value "Employee Created"
the employee id "Employee.employee_id" is stored as a global variable to be used for other calls
a request is prepared to get the employee
a GET call is made to retrieve the created employee
the status code for the get the created employee is 200
the employee we are getting having ID "employee.employee_id" must match with the globally stored employee id
the retrieved data at "employee" object matches the data used to create the employee having employee id "employee.employee_id"
